<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Health Center</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #0f3c74;
            --primary-dark: #0b2a52;
            --accent: #24b8b5;
            --ink: #111827;
            --muted: #6b7280;
            --surface: #ffffff;
            --bg: #f4f8fc;
            --border: #dbe7f3;
            --shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(15, 60, 116, 0.16);
        }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--ink);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container { width: min(1100px, 92%); margin: 0 auto; }
        main { padding: 56px 0; }
        section { margin-bottom: 18px; }
        .card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 18px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            padding: 26px;
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.6vw, 2.4rem);
        }
        h2 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 1.35rem;
        }
        p { margin: 0 0 14px; color: #334155; }
        .grid-2 {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 16px;
        }
        .pill {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: #f9fcff;
            color: #0f172a;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 6px 6px 0 0;
        }
        .team-grid, .doctor-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 14px;
        }
        .person {
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 16px;
            background: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .person-photo {
            margin: -4px -4px 14px -4px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            overflow: hidden;
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #eef4fb, #f9fcff);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .person-photo img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            display: block;
        }
        .person .name { font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; }
        .person .role { color: var(--muted); font-weight: 600; }
        .person .meta { margin-top: 8px; color: #334155; font-size: 0.95rem; flex: 1; }
        .banner {
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 22px;
            color: #e8f2ff;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(15, 60, 116, 0.95), rgba(11, 42, 82, 0.88)), url('/images/Background.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }
        .banner h1 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .banner p { color: #d6e5fb; max-width: 820px; }
        @media (max-width: 860px) {
            .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
{% include 'partials/public_nav.html.twig' %}

<main>
    <div class="container">
        <section class="banner">
            <h1>About Health Center</h1>
            <p>
                We provide a secure, clinic‑ready platform that improves scheduling, communication, and record handling—helping care teams deliver faster and more consistent patient service.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
            <h2>What “Health Care” Means Here</h2>
            <p>
                Our system is designed around the core clinic workflow: booking and managing appointments, coordinating schedules, tracking services provided, and supporting timely follow‑ups.
                It promotes a reliable patient experience while reducing administrative overhead.
            </p>
            <div>
                <span class="pill">Secure access</span>
                <span class="pill">Efficient scheduling</span>
                <span class="pill">Clinic-ready workflow</span>
                <span class="pill">Mobile-friendly</span>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
            <div class="grid-2">
                <div>
                    <h2>Mission</h2>
                    <p>
                        To deliver patient‑centered care through practical digital tools that make clinic processes faster, clearer, and more dependable.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h2>Vision</h2>
                    <p>
                        A community where every patient can access quality primary care with well‑organized services and seamless coordination.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
            <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
            <p>People behind the platform and clinic operations.</p>
            <div class="team-grid">
                <div class="person">
                    <div class="person-photo">
                        <img src="/images/teammie.jpg" alt="Portrait placeholder for Clinic Administrator" width="280" height="280" loading="lazy">
                    </div>
                    <div class="name">Clinic Administrator</div>
                    <div class="role">Operations Lead</div>
                    <div class="meta">Oversees clinic workflows, scheduling policies, and system compliance.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="person">
                    <div class="person-photo">
                        <img src="/images/teammie.jpg" alt="Portrait placeholder for Front Desk Coordinator" width="280" height="280" loading="lazy">
                    </div>
                    <div class="name">Front Desk Coordinator</div>
                    <div class="role">Patient Services</div>
                    <div class="meta">Supports appointment requests, patient inquiries, and day-to-day coordination.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="person">
                    <div class="person-photo">
                        <img src="/images/teammie.jpg" alt="Portrait placeholder for Clinical Staff" width="280" height="280" loading="lazy">
                    </div>
                    <div class="name">Clinical Staff</div>
                    <div class="role">Care Team</div>
                    <div class="meta">Assists with service delivery, documentation, and patient follow-ups.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="person">
                    <div class="person-photo">
                        <img src="/images/teammie.jpg" alt="Portrait placeholder for System Support" width="280" height="280" loading="lazy">
                    </div>
                    <div class="name">System Support</div>
                    <div class="role">Technical Support</div>
                    <div class="meta">Maintains system reliability, security updates, and platform improvements.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p style="margin: 14px 0 0; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted);">Replace the placeholder art in <code>public/images/team/</code> with your team photos (same filenames, JPG or WebP).</p>
        </section>

        <section class="card">
            <h2>Doctors</h2>
            <p>Our current directory of available doctors.</p>
            {% if doctors is empty %}
                <p style="color: var(--muted);">No doctors are available yet.</p>
            {% else %}
                <div class="doctor-grid">
                    {% for doctor in doctors %}
                        <div class="person">
                            <div class="name">{{ doctor.name }}</div>
                            <div class="role">{{ doctor.specialization }}</div>
                            <div class="meta">
                                <div><strong>Email:</strong> {{ doctor.email }}</div>
                                <div><strong>Contact:</strong> {{ doctor.contactNumber }}</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
            {% endif %}
        </section>
    </div>
</main>
</body>
</html>
